data.description: Well maintained, cozy family home on friendly, tree lined street. This classic ranch design features 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. Stainless appliances in kitchen and brand new hood vent over the stove. Spacious dining and living areas center around stone, wood burning fireplace. A memorable focal point for holiday celebrations. Open concept is great for entertaining friends and family. Spend summers grilling on the covered patio and enjoying the tree shaded, fenced back yard. Brand new front steel screen door provides character and security. The inviting front porch is perfect for a cold evening drink and socializing. Features alley access to garage in back. The perfect little neighborhood, tucked away, with a short drive to many major connecting arteries and roadways.
